document_data.Society and Religion:
Some cath shee consented to becoming companions to [[green elves]] and [[silver elves]]. They were persuadable, but could change their mind several months later.

[[Skinwalker]]s of [[Rillifane Rallathil]] could have cath shee as their totem animal.{{cite book/Elves of Evermeet|109}}{{cite book/Demihuman Deities|124}} Priests of [[Nobanion]] could transform into cath shee by using [[Feline form]].

Several [[Seldarine]] gods were served by cath shee, such as [[Eilistraee]],{{cite book/Demihuman Deities|14}} [[Corellon]],{{cite book/Demihuman Deities|101}} [[Erevan Ilesere]],{{cite book/Demihuman Deities|109}} [[Hanali Celanil]]{{cite book/Demihuman Deities|115}} and Rillifane Rallathil.{{cite book/Demihuman Deities|122}}
